    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>    /* 全局样式 */    body {        font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;        margin: 0;        padding: 0;        background-color: #f8f9fa;        color: #333;        line-height: 1.5;    }            .container {        max-width: 1200px;        margin: 0 auto;        padding: 0 15px;    }            /* 基础视频样式 */    .video-item {        position: relative;        width: 100%;        overflow: hidden;        border-radius: 6px;        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);        background: #000;    }    .video-item iframe {        position: absolute;        top: 0; left: 0;        width: 100%; height: 100%;        border: none;    }    /* PC端布局 - 第一行2个，其余3个 */    .video-gallery-first {        display: grid;        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);        gap: 10px;        margin: 25px 0;    }    .video-gallery-first .video-item {        padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 比例 */    }            .video-gallery-rest {        display: grid;        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);        gap: 10px;        margin: 10px 0;    }    .video-gallery-rest .video-item {        padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 比例 */    }    /* 移动端布局 - 统一每行2个，第一行视频较小 */    @media (max-width: 768px) {        /* 减小移动端字体大小 */        body {            font-size: 15px;        }                    .hero-banner h1 {            font-size: 1.8rem !important;        }                    .hero-banner p {            font-size: 1rem !important;        }                    .section-title h2 span {            font-size: 1.4rem !important;        }                    .competition-cards .card-header h3 {            font-size: 1.3rem !important;        }                    .team-card h3 {            font-size: 1.2rem !important;        }                    .training-section h3 {            font-size: 1.1rem !important;        }                    .cta-section h2 {            font-size: 1.6rem !important;        }                    .cta-section p {            font-size: 1rem !important;        }                    /* 调整移动端间距 */        .hero-banner {            padding: 20px 15px !important;            margin-bottom: 20px !important;        }                    .section-title {            margin: 25px 0 20px !important;        }                    .competition-cards {            gap: 15px !important;            margin-bottom: 25px !important;        }                    .card {            min-width: 100% !important;        }                    .team-grid {            gap: 15px !important;            margin-bottom: 30px !important;        }                    .training-section {            padding: 20px !important;            margin: 25px 0 !important;        }                    .cta-section {            padding: 30px 15px !important;            margin: 30px 0 !important;        }                    /* 移动端卡片内部调整 */        .card-body {            padding: 15px !important;        }                    .team-card > div:last-child {            padding: 15px !important;        }                    /* 移动端视频布局调整 */        .video-gallery-first,        .video-gallery-rest {            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);            gap: 8px;            margin: 15px 0;        }                    /* 第一行视频较小（4:3比例） */        .video-gallery-first .video-item {            padding-bottom: 75%; /* 4:3 比例 */        }                    /* 其余行保持正常大小 */        .video-gallery-rest .video-item {            padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 比例 */        }    }    /* 超小屏幕优化 */    @media (max-width: 400px) {        body {            font-size: 14px;        }                    .hero-banner h1 {            font-size: 1.6rem !important;        }                    .section-title h2 span {            font-size: 1.3rem !important;            padding: 0 10px !important;        }                    .video-gallery-first,        .video-gallery-rest {            gap: 6px;        }                    /* 第一行视频更小 */        .video-gallery-first .video-item {            padding-bottom: 65%; /* 更紧凑的比例 */        }                    .team-grid {            grid-template-columns: 1fr;        }    }    /* 其他原有样式 */    .hero-banner {        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #4a6491 100%);        border-radius: 12px;        padding: 30px;        margin: 0 0 30px;        color: white;        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);    }            .hero-banner > div {        max-width: 800px;        margin: 0 auto;        text-align: center;    }            .hero-banner h1 {        margin-top: 0;        font-size: 2.5rem;        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);    }            .hero-banner p {        font-size: 1.4rem;        margin-bottom: 20px;        opacity: 0.9;    }            .hero-banner > div > div {        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);        border-radius: 50px;        padding: 15px 30px;        display: inline-block;    }            .hero-banner > div > div p {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.1rem;    }            .section-title {        text-align: center;        margin: 40px 0 25px;    }            .section-title h2 {        display: inline-block;        margin: 0;        padding: 0 20px;        position: relative;    }            .section-title h2 span {        background: white;        position: relative;        z-index: 2;        padding: 0 15px;    }            .section-title h2 div {        position: absolute;        height: 3px;        background: linear-gradient(to right, #d9534f, #5bc0de);        width: 100%;        top: 50%;        left: 0;        transform: translateY(-50%);        z-index: 1;    }            .section-title p {        margin-top: 10px;        color: #6c757d;    }            .competition-cards {        display: flex;        flex-wrap: wrap;        gap: 20px;        justify-content: center;        margin-bottom: 40px;    }            .competition-cards a {        text-decoration: none;        flex: 1;        min-width: 300px;        max-width: 450px;    }            .card {        border-radius: 12px;        overflow: hidden;        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);        transition: transform 0.3s;        cursor: pointer;    }            .card:hover {        transform: translateY(-5px);    }            .card-header {        padding: 20px;        color: white;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        gap: 15px;    }            .card-header h3 {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.5rem;    }            .card-body {        padding: 25px;        background: white;    }            .card-body p:first-child {        font-size: 1.1rem;        margin-top: 0;    }            .card-body > div {        margin-top: 20px;        background: #f8f9fa;        padding: 12px;        border-radius: 8px;    }            .card-body > div p {        margin: 0;        font-size: 0.9rem;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        gap: 8px;    }            .card-body > div p span {        color: white;        width: 24px;        height: 24px;        border-radius: 50%;        display: inline-flex;        align-items: center;        justify-content: center;    }            .team-grid {        display: grid;        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));        gap: 25px;        margin-bottom: 50px;    }            .team-card-link {        text-decoration: none;    }            .team-card {        background: white;        border-radius: 12px;        overflow: hidden;        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);        transition: transform 0.3s;        cursor: pointer;    }            .team-card:hover {        transform: translateY(-3px);    }            .team-card > div:first-child {        padding: 18px;        color: white;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        gap: 12px;    }            .team-card h3 {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.4rem;    }            .team-card > div:last-child {        padding: 22px;    }            .team-card > div:last-child > p:first-child {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.1rem;    }            .team-card > div:last-child > div {        margin-top: 15px;        background: #f8f9fa;        padding: 12px;        border-radius: 8px;        border-left: 3px solid;    }            .team-card > div:last-child > div p {        margin: 0;        font-size: 0.95rem;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        gap: 8px;    }            .training-section {        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);        border-radius: 12px;        padding: 30px;        margin: 40px 0;        text-align: center;        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);    }            .training-section > div {        max-width: 800px;        margin: 0 auto;    }            .training-section > div > div {        display: inline-flex;        background: #5bc0de;        color: white;        padding: 8px 20px;        border-radius: 50px;        margin-bottom: 20px;        align-items: center;        gap: 10px;    }            .training-section h3 {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.3rem;    }            .training-section p {        font-size: 1.2rem;        line-height: 1.6;    }            .training-section > div > div:last-child {        display: flex;        justify-content: center;        gap: 15px;        flex-wrap: wrap;        margin-top: 25px;    }            .training-section > div > div:last-child > div {        background: white;        padding: 12px 20px;        border-radius: 8px;        box-shadow: 0 3px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);    }            .training-section > div > div:last-child > div p {        margin: 0;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        gap: 8px;    }            .cta-section {        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);        color: white;        padding: 50px 20px;        border-radius: 12px;        text-align: center;        margin: 50px 0;        position: relative;        overflow: hidden;    }            .cta-section div:first-child,    .cta-section div:nth-child(2) {        position: absolute;        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);        border-radius: 50%;    }            .cta-section div:first-child {        top: -50px;        right: -50px;        width: 200px;        height: 200px;    }            .cta-section div:nth-child(2) {        bottom: -30px;        left: -30px;        width: 150px;        height: 150px;    }            .cta-section > div:last-child {        position: relative;        z-index: 2;        max-width: 800px;        margin: 0 auto;    }            .cta-section h2 {        margin-top: 0;        margin-bottom: 20px;        font-size: 2.2rem;        text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);    }            .cta-section p {        font-size: 1.25rem;        line-height: 1.6;        margin-bottom: 30px;    }            .cta-section > div:last-child > div {        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);        border: 2px dashed rgba(255,255,255,0.3);        border-radius: 12px;        padding: 25px;        margin-top: 20px;    }            .cta-section > div:last-child > div p {        margin: 0;        font-size: 1.4rem;        font-weight: bold;        display: flex;        align-items: center;        justify-content: center;        gap: 15px;    }</style></head><body><div class="container">    <div class="hero-banner">        <div>            <h1>欢迎加入RC机器人协会！</h1>            <p>这里是机器人爱好者的乐园，更是你通往技术巅峰的起点站！</p>            <div>                <p>各位同学大家好！欢迎来到福建理工大学学生RC机器人协会！</p>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class="section-title">        <h2>            <span>双赛道国家级赛事平台</span>            <div></div>        </h2>        <p>我们协会分为两大核心部门，分别负责：</p>    </div>    <div class="competition-cards">        <a href="https://www.robomaster.com/zh-CN" target="_blank">            <div class="card">                <div class="card-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9534f 0%, #c12e2a 100%);">                    <div></div>                    <h3>RoboMaster机甲大师赛</h3>                </div>                <div class="card-body">                    <p>全国对抗性机器人赛事</p>                    <p>无论你钟情于激烈的红蓝对抗...</p>                    <div>                        <p>                            <span style="background: #d9534f;">!</span>                            战术对抗 · 团队作战 · 实时竞技                        </p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="https://www.cnrobocon.net/" target="_blank">            <div class="card">                <div class="card-header" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5bc0de 0%, #2a96b5 100%);">                    <div></div>                    <h3>RoboCon亚太机器人大赛</h3>                </div>                <div class="card-body">                    <p>创意任务型机器人挑战</p>                    <p>还是偏爱创意的机械协作...</p>                    <div>                        <p>                            <span style="background: #5bc0de;">!</span>                            创新设计 · 任务解决 · 技术融合                        </p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>    </div>    <div class="video-gallery-first">        <div class="video-item"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114617980291815&bvid=BV1SW78zFEnq&cid=30297427491&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>        <div class="video-item"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=115117975019394&bvid=BV1jhhizoErD&cid=32054838033&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>    </div>    <div class="video-gallery-rest">        <div class="video-item"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114971912445859&bvid=BV1CgtVzcE9Y&cid=31489592502&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>        <div class="video-item"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=114525906933503&bvid=BV1NQJTz8EsZ&cid=30015818557&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>        <div class="video-item"><iframe src="//player.bilibili.com/player.html?isOutside=true&aid=1253425276&bvid=BV1VJ4m1H7Ft&cid=1514037188&p=1" scrolling="no" border="0" frameborder="no" framespacing="0" allowfullscreen="true"></iframe></div>    </div>    <div class="section-title">        <h2>            <span>六大组别开放招募</span>            <div></div>        </h2>        <p>选择你感兴趣的领域，开启机器人技术之旅</p>    </div>            <div class="team-grid">        <a href="/groups/mechanical" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5cb85c 0%, #449d44 100%);">                    <div>⚙️</div>                    <h3>机械组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>从CAD建模到实体搭建，亲手打造钢铁之躯！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #5cb85c;">                        <p style="color: #5cb85c;">掌握技能：SolidWorks · 机械设计 · 3D打印</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="/groups/electronic-control" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0ad4e 0%, #ec971f 100%);">                    <div>🔌</div>                    <h3>电控组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>玩转电路板与代码，赋予机器人灵魂与动力！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #f0ad4e;">                        <p style="color: #f0ad4e;">掌握技能：STM32 · C/C++ · 嵌入式开发</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="/groups/hardware" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d9534f 0%, #c9302c 100%);">                    <div>🔋</div>                    <h3>硬件组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>硬件选型、焊接调试，构建稳定的电子神经系统！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #d9534f;">                        <p style="color: #d9534f;">掌握技能：PCB设计 · 电路调试 · 焊接技术</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="/groups/vision" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5bc0de 0%, #2aabd2 100%);">                    <div>👁️</div>                    <h3>视觉组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>机器视觉算法研发，让机器人拥有"火眼金睛"！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #5bc0de;">                        <p style="color: #5bc0de;">掌握技能：OpenCV · 深度学习 · 图像处理</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="/groups/media" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #337ab7 0%, #2a5d8a 100%);">                    <div>📸</div>                    <h3>宣传组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>用镜头和文字记录团队成长，打造协会高光时刻！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #337ab7;">                        <p style="color: #337ab7;">掌握技能：摄影剪辑 · 新媒体运营 · 内容创作</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>        <a href="/groups/operations" class="team-card-link">            <div class="team-card">                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8e44ad 0%, #732d91 100%);">                    <div>📊</div>                    <h3>运营组</h3>                </div>                <div>                    <p>赛事统筹、资源管理，保障战队高效运转！</p>                    <div style="border-left-color: #8e44ad;">                        <p style="color: #8e44ad;">掌握技能：项目管理 · 资源协调 · 活动策划</p>                    </div>                </div>            </div>        </a>    </div>    <div class="training-section">        <div>            <div>                <div>🚀</div>                <h3>零基础？别担心！</h3>            </div>            <p>无论你是零基础小白还是有一定基础的同学，我们都有经验丰富的学长学姐手把手带教——从基础工具使用到复杂系统设计，从小组实战项目到全国赛场历练，助你逐步成长为独当一面的技术大牛！</p>            <div>                <div>                    <p><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 阶梯式培训体系</p>                </div>                <div>                    <p><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 竞赛项目驱动</p>                </div>                <div>                    <p><span style="color: #5cb85c;">✓</span> 手把手教学制度</p>                </div>            </div>        </div>    </div>    <div class="cta-section">        <div></div>        <div></div>        <div>            <h2>在这里，你不仅能收获硬核的工程技能</h2>            <p>更能结识志同道合的伙伴，共同经历机器人从图纸到赛场的蜕变过程！每一次调试的坚持、每一次胜利的欢呼，都将成为你大学生活中最难忘的回忆！</p>            <div>                <p>招新进行中！立即加入开启你的机器人征程</p>            </div>        </div>    </div></div><script>    // 响应式调整：在超小屏幕上将团队卡片改为单列    function adjustTeamGrid() {        const teamGrid = document.querySelector('.team-grid');        if (!teamGrid) return;                    if (window.innerWidth <= 400) {            teamGrid.style.gridTemplateColumns = '1fr';        } else {            teamGrid.style.gridTemplateColumns = 'repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr))';        }    }            // 初始调整    window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', adjustTeamGrid);            // 窗口大小变化时调整    window.addEventListener('resize', adjustTeamGrid);</script>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
